casebody.data:
William H. EVANS, Jr., petitioner,
v.
William T. MARSHALL, Judge, Court of Common Pleas of Ohio, Scioto County. No. 13-5761. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013.

Case below, 984 N.E.2d 1100.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Ohio dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
